synopsis: Following the battle with King Ashura, Fey's weakened powers lead Kurogane to make a stunning sacrifice. After the group arrives in the his homeland, Kurogane must face a foe with a very familiar face.
Syaoran once more faces Syaoran, and Sakura is wounded during the battle.  Yet, once more, things are not what they seem - Syaoran is not the only traveler who seems to have a clone!
